OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,6,Fotherwise rather cloudy. There will be
OL,7,Fa few showers, some of which could
OL,8,Fturn heavy over Dumfriesshire and the
OL,9,FBorders for a time.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe Borders and East Lothian
OL,12,Fwill stay cloudy with some patchy
OL,13,Frain, perhaps becoming more persistent
OL,14,Fovernight. The west will be dry with
OL,15,Fsome clear periods over Galloway.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy with some
OL,18,Fpatchy rain, though more persistent at
OL,19,Ffirst over the Borders. Best of any
OL,20,Fbrighter weather over Galloway.
OL,21,FColder, especially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
